    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 straight-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to preserve chassis integrity. The suspension architecture remains precise, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for optimal kinematic feedback. While presenting in honest condition with minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust and the power delivery is linear. This is a technically sound specimen for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
