      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been meticulously cared for by a non-smoker. The exterior retains its deep luster, though a close inspection reveals the minor stone chips expected from highway driving, and there is a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all dashboard electronics, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has a full service history with recent oil and filter changes, and the brake pads were replaced just 3,000 miles ago. The transmission shifts smoothly through every gear, and the engine idle is whisper-quiet. It sits on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is an honest, dependable car that drives as beautifully as it looks, perfect for someone who values a well-documented maintenance history and a vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
